overview: Dakota is stuck in detention because she got caught checking out the boys in the locker room. Professor Drake thinks she's too innocent to do such a thing, but he's about to be proven wrong. Marina doesn't take school too seriously and as a result hasn't graduated yet. She knows there is one surefire way to make sure Mr. Carson lets her pass this time around. Alina is a confident student who always gets what she wants. In this case, it's a hot romp at school with her professor and she makes sure she gets satisfied. With a bad record for violence, Miko is on the verge of getting expelled from school permanently. She begs Principal Jacobs to let her stay, which he will do on only one sexy condition.
title: Corrupt Schoolgirls 10
